- [x] Verify multi-colored vintage books -> Verified. Books have rich, warm colors, decorative lines, and embossed/ribbed styles.
- [x] Verify distinct label blocks -> Verified. Clean labels like "Movies & Shows", "Games", "Music", etc., are nicely integrated.
- [x] Verify gold emblems -> Verified. Books feature gold emblems (crowns/stars) on the spines.
