## Detailed Visual Findings & Interactive Experience
1. **Interactive Book Hover & Click**:
   - Books highlight and tilt beautifully on hover.
   - Clicking a book spine brings up a high-fidelity leather-bound, gold-embossed cover modal with full titles (e.g. "The Matrix", "Dune").
   - Clicking "Click to Open" opens an elegant, editorial double-page skeuomorphic layout complete with badge categories, golden star ratings, descriptive summaries, illustrations/images, and pagination navigation.
   - Modals function perfectly and close cleanly when clicking "Close" or "Return to Shelf".
2. **Visual Shelf Layout**:
   - All columns (6-5-6 layout) show dynamic, asymmetric compartments.
   - The double-height "Apps Built" middle compartment displays the beautiful leaning photo illustration and scaled-down bunny plush ornament.
   - The bottom-left and bottom-right floor plants add a beautiful grounding cozy look.
   - Note: Because of strict scroll-locking and dynamic grid ratios, some of the absolute-positioned vintage book spines extend/render beyond their individual shelf dividers, creating a unique stylized vintage vertical overlap look.

